# Informal Signage: Air Warning

**Location / Context:** Scrawled on the bulkhead doors leading to Docking Bay 4.
**Visual Description:** Jagged lettering, warning color (like faded orange or red) if available.

**English Text:**
> __trust#NEG#CL2 air#CL9 LOC bay#CL5 four.#CL4 bring#IMP scrubber#CL9 POSS2SG or choke#IMP LOC exhaust#CL9 inner.#POSS#CL2__
"Don't trust the air in Bay 4. Bring your own scrubber or choke on inner exhaust."
